                        US AIRWAYS VACATIONS

US Airways Vacations is pleased to offer Dominican Republic land packages to provide a complete vacation experience.

Vacations include accommodations at a variety of hotels for up to 21 nights; hotel taxes and service charges.  A variety of optional features including sightseeing tours are available.

EXPERIENCE DOMINICAN REPUBLIC!
